column5: Ok, so I just recieved a new Christmas present, and its a # 11 Purple Clown Flash, Rapala Deep Tail Dancer!  So here is my updated Rapala selection of lures!  Once again, I am open to any suggestions on lures!        ........ lol, who knows what lures I may get later on today?
Nice looking lure buddy, as i said before, more x-raps.  UhOh  the rapala count is now 10! Your 1 behind me bud...and as said before to you if it's fishing related take a pic and send it to me!!!
The only fishing related stuff I got so far is a salmon magnet, the lure, and a book called "Incredible Fishing Stories" ... this is what the book looks like...
The book has like over 100 different world record fish, fish legends and myths, reported "sea (fish) monster" sightings and everything bout good ole' fishing stories
Hey Dude....   Don't be afraid to lop in some White Big-O's in to your collection
I got a Mustang floater coat
I got that book a few years back for Xmas, it has a tonne of pretty cool stories in there all documented true as well
i like the ripplin redfin.   a white one with a pink line down the side always manages to find its way onto my rod by the end of a day on the water
i just realized that my Rapala Jointed Shad Rap is not pictured, its somewhere in my garage, so once i find it, ill add it to the collection!!!
